OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with the morning cloud
OL,6,Fburning off to leave a warm or very
OL,7,Fwarm day with sunny spells. Fresher
OL,8,Faround some coasts with sea breezes
OL,9,Fdeveloping.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA fine end to the day and
OL,12,Fstaying mainly dry overnight.
OL,13,FThickening cloud could bring patchy
OL,14,Frain. Winds mostly light.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FMainly dry and bright with
OL,17,Fhazy sunshine and very warm or hot.
OL,18,FOccasional thicker cloud could give
OL,19,Fthe odd burst of rain later. Light
OL,20,Fwinds with sea breezes possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
